recordedBy: Eiten, G; Sendullsky, T; Sendulsky, T
locality: 5,5km S & 1,9km E of main plaza in city of São José dos Campos (along road to Paraibuna)
occurrenceRemarks: Grass in small clumps with 3-7 flowering stems per clump; Cerrado low woodland with trees 3-5m tall 5-15m apart, scattered shrubs & grass. Soil light brown fine sandy clay

locality: Disjunct cerrado of several hundred sq. km surrounded by former forest. Ca. 7 km S of main plaza of São José dos Campos, along road to Paraibuna
occurrenceRemarks: Cerrado with trees to 5 m. tall, 5-15 m. apart, plus scattered shrubs and grasses (mostly Melinus minutiflora and Aristida pallens). Soil light brown fine sandy clay
